title: 2014 Holden Commodore SV6 Storm VF Auto MY14
description:
The 2014 Holden Commodore SV6 Storm offers Australian-built performance with everyday practicality. Powered by a 3.6L V6 engine and 6-speed sports automatic, it blends power, comfort, and technology in a stylish sedan package.
3.6L V6 petrol engine
6-speed sports automatic transmission
Rear-wheel drive
Storm edition styling with unique badging
Leather-trimmed sports seats with Storm embroidery
Touchscreen infotainment system with satellite navigation
Bluetooth connectivity and USB input
Reverse camera with rear parking sensors
Multi-function steering wheel with cruise control
Dual-zone climate control
18-inch alloy wheels
Fog lights and LED daytime running lights
Sports suspension
Large boot with split-fold rear seats
Comprehensive safety with multiple airbags, ABS, and stability control

A true Australian favourite, this SV6 Storm delivers sporty performance and modern features in a well-balanced package
